<br>
No, absolutely not.  There is no PVP in the game (at this time) so high level players cannot hurt you.  PVP is actually programmed into the game and may be unlocked in a later patch.  In fact most high level players are extremely helpful and generous.  When you die, a WHM with Raise or Raise II will generally take 10-30 minutes out of his time to bring you back to life.  The importer LS's (Linkshells) are also very helpful.  High level players help beginners with any questions or problems with quests.  Playing with others and fighting alongside friends is the best part of the game.<br>
<br>
Lag is usually not a problem if you have cable internet or better.  On a modem you can still get by but its harder, but that is the same with most every online game.  Usually lag comes in 10-second long spurts every 30 minutes or so.  When the server is crowded at peak times and in crowded areas, lag is a bit more of a problem.  But overall with cable internet you don't need to worry about it at all.<br>
<br>
